      "raw_text": "COLFAx. Wash. Oct. 12.--One of\nthe largest crowds ever seen in town\nIs here In attendance at the opening\nOf the whitman county fair today.\n\n\nAt the fair grounds the final\ntouches are being given xhe numerous\ndisplays and the blooded stock Is be-\ning received. The fruit exhibit now\narranged will be the best ever seen\nin whitman county."
